settings.question: How do I place an order?
settings.answer:
Visit Track Order to check the status of an order at any time.

Skyline dispatches many items within 1 business day from when the order is placed. However, certain items may take longer to process. Look for the shipping information located on the product page to see when a specific item is expected to ship. *Note: Some products will also include an "Expected Arrival" time frame.

Upon the shipment of an item, an email notification will be sent with the tracking number and an estimated delivery date. Once shipped, most items are delivered within 2-5 business days.
